  </TextSection>

  <TextSection>
    <h2 class="text-base sm:text-lg pt-6">
      How do you stay motivated to read a book?
    </h2>
    <p class="">
      Reading something that resonates with you and leaves you feeling
      invigorated can be a powerful motivating factor.
    </p>
    <p class="">But how do you stay motivated to read a book?</p>
    <p>
      One tip is to find a book that aligns with your goals and interests, so
      you're more likely to be invested in the content.
    </p>
    <p class="">
      Moreover, setting aside some dedicated time for reading every day can help
      you build a habit and stay consistent.
    </p>
    <p>
      Ultimately, if you're willing to put in the effort to find the right book
      and commit to a regular reading routine, the benefits of motivational
      literature can be truly life-changing.
    </p>

    <div class="flex justify-center items-center gap-5 flex-wrap pb-6">
